post.description:
Convert data between JSON and other formats (YAML, TOML, XML, CSV). This endpoint is useful for data transformation and format conversion.
## Features - Supports multiple data formats (JSON, YAML, TOML, XML, CSV) - Various output styles (pretty, compact, single_line) - Handles complex nested structures
## CURL Example ```bash curl -X POST https://api.assisted.space/v2/tools/process/format \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -H "X-API-Key: your_api_key" \
  -d '{
    "data": {
      "name": "John Doe",
      "age": 30,
      "address": {
        "street": "123 Main St",
        "city": "Anytown",
        "zip": "12345"
      },
      "hobbies": ["reading", "running", "coding"]
    },
    "target_format": "yaml",
    "style": "pretty"
  }'
```

